stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Orient

    state Orient {
        [*] --> CheckIntent
        CheckIntent: Classify task (in llm_request, no tool)
        CheckIntent --> ReadArch: structural
        CheckIntent --> SkipArch: local change
        ReadArch: Read ARCHITECTURE.md<br/>=== 46x | 0.1 min ===
        SkipArch: (skip)
        ReadArch --> [*]
        SkipArch --> [*]
    }

    Orient --> WorktreeSetup: isolated / parallel work
    Orient --> Locate: in-place work

    state WorktreeSetup {
        [*] --> BranchOffMain
        BranchOffMain: git worktree, branch off main (NOT current branch)
        BranchOffMain --> PinSHA
        PinSHA: Pin integration SHA in agent prompt
        PinSHA --> Install
        Install: pnpm install IN the worktree<br/>=== 45x | 2.5 min ===
        Install --> InstallCheck
        state InstallCheck <<choice>>
        InstallCheck --> Install: missing -> edits would no-op
        InstallCheck --> [*]: deps present
    }
    WorktreeSetup --> Locate

    state Locate {
        [*] --> PlanSearch
        PlanSearch: Plan the query (in llm_request, no tool)
        PlanSearch --> FireOnce
        FireOnce: ONE broad search (Grep/Glob/Explore)<br/>=== 225x | 0.9 min | 116k tok ===
        FireOnce --> HaveSites
        state HaveSites <<choice>>
        HaveSites --> [*]: sites found
        HaveSites --> Widen: empty result
        Widen: Broaden scope (still one shot)
        Widen --> [*]
    }
    Locate --> ChangeCycle

    state ChangeCycle {
        [*] --> Read
        Read: Read target file FULLY<br/>=== 1163x | 0.5 min | 592k tok ===
        Read --> Edit
        Edit: Author / batch independent edits<br/>=== EDIT 1566x | 28.6 min | 928k tok ===<br/>=== AUTHOR 295x | 4.8 min | 633k tok ===
        state EditResult <<choice>>
        Edit --> EditResult
        EditResult --> Read: rejected 56x (unread / stale)
        EditResult --> MoreEdits: applied 1510x
        state MoreEdits <<choice>>
        MoreEdits --> Edit: more edits queued
        MoreEdits --> BashMutate: file-mutating Bash needed
        MoreEdits --> Run: edits done
        BashMutate: sed / perl / git mv / rm<br/>=== 155x | 2.2 min | 154k tok ===
        BashMutate --> Read: re-read (read-cache invalidated)
        Run: Run NARROWEST check<br/>=== 666x | 13.4 min | 436k tok ===
        state RunResult <<choice>>
        Run --> RunResult
        RunResult --> Read: fail 39x -> fix
        RunResult --> [*]: pass 793x
    }
    ChangeCycle --> Validation

    state Validation {
        [*] --> Verify
        Verify: Verify behavior vs goal<br/>=== 140x | 5.3 min | 20k tok ===
        state VerifyResult <<choice>>
        Verify --> VerifyResult
        VerifyResult --> Reenter: wrong 44x
        VerifyResult --> CoverageCheck: matches goal 262x
        Reenter: back to ChangeCycle (re-read first)
        Reenter --> [*]
        CoverageCheck: Is file TS/JS? (judgment, no tool)
        state CovChoice <<choice>>
        CoverageCheck --> CovChoice
        CovChoice --> HandVerify: non-TS 57 files (NO hook)
        CovChoice --> Gate: TS/JS 192 files (hook-covered)
        HandVerify: Verify by hand (eyeball, no tool)
        HandVerify --> Gate
        Gate: pnpm check (full backstop)<br/>=== 227x | 28.7 min | 55k tok ===
        state GateResult <<choice>>
        Gate --> GateResult
        GateResult --> Reenter: red 38x
        GateResult --> [*]: green 189x
    }

    Validation --> ChangeCycle: re-enter on failure
    Validation --> Ship: green + verified

    state Ship {
        [*] --> Push
        Push: Commit + push branch<br/>=== 90x | 7.5 min | (vcs 70k tok) ===
        Push --> OpenPR
        OpenPR: Open PR (gh pr)<br/>=== 35x | 4.1 min ===
        OpenPR --> HandVerifyPrompt
        HandVerifyPrompt: Attach clean-session verification prompt (generation, no tool)
        HandVerifyPrompt --> [*]
    }

    Ship --> Review
    Review: STOP - maintainer approves and merges (human, off-trace)
    Review --> [*]
